data.description:
This Nice modern 3 bed 3 bath with a bonus room for all your family fun.This home has an open floor plan with living room opens to kitchen.
Nice 4 foot island sets in the middle.We’ve updated appliances,light fixtures and new laminate flooring.
Bonus room has 2 ceiling fans and a bathroom.
The bonus room leads outside to a covered patio and a large beautiful deck with a fenced in back yard and shed for extra storage space.
This home is Sold AS IS
